<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Vyrion — Transparency Intelligence</title>

<style>
/* Base Reset & Body */
body {
    margin: 0;
    background-color: #05070a;
    color: #e8f0f2;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Container */
.container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
}

/* Headings */
h1, h2, h3 {
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Header */
.header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #00f0ff;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.tagline {
    color: #7f8c8d;
    margin-top: 5px;
    font-size: 14px;
}

/* Cards */
.card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

/* Score Styling */
.score {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px);
    color: #00ff9c;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #ccc;
    margin-top: 5px;
}

/* Tags */
.tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border: 1px solid #00f0ff;
    color: #00f0ff;
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    margin-right: 5px;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

/* Grid Modules */
.grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}

.module {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 15px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 6px;
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
    margin-top: 60px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #888;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 20px;
}

/* Responsive Adjustments */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .container {
        padding: 20px 15px;
    }
    .logo {
        font-size: 20px;
    }
    .tagline {
        font-size: 12px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">VYRION</div>
        <div class="tagline">Transparency Intelligence System</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Definition -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Definition</h2>
        <p>Vyrion Score = A weighted transparency index measuring verifiable ESG signal integrity across 8 modules.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Example Company Score -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Company Profile — Example</h2>
        <div class="score">74</div>
        <div class="label">Vyrion Score</div>
        <div class="tag">Confidence: Medium</div>
        <div class="tag">Updated: March 2026</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Module Breakdown -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Module Breakdown</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="module">Environmental<br><strong>68</strong></div>
            <div class="module">Social<br><strong>72</strong></div>
            <div class="module">Governance<br><strong>79</strong></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Issues -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Key Issues</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Emission data lacks third-party verification</li>
            <li>Labor audit inconsistencies identified</li>
            <li>Governance transparency above industry baseline</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Data Verification -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Data Verification Layer</h2>
        <p><strong>Claim:</strong> Emissions reduced by 12%</p>
        <p><strong>Source:</strong> 2023 Sustainability Report (pg. 42)</p>
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> Self-Reported</p>
        <p><strong>Confidence:</strong> Medium</p>
        <p><strong>Updated:</strong> March 2024</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Methodology -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Methodology</h2>
        <p>Vyrion Methodology v1.0 is a fixed, version-controlled framework. No scoring changes occur without public updates.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This analysis is based on publicly available data.</p>
        <p>Vyrion is a methodology-based scoring system.</p>
        <p>This content is not financial advice.</p>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>}

